{"lemma":"حَقْوَيْ","slug":"حَقْوَيْ","root":"ح.ق.#","root_slug":"ح-ق-_","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-ق-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n8659","n8660"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%8E%D9%82%D9%92%D9%88%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%92"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n8659","headword_ar":"حَقْوٌ","root":"Hqw","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"waist;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaSorN","text_ar":"خَصْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) [or] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the side,"},{"kind":"text","text":"TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"where the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"waist-wrapper called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_izaAr","text_ar":"اـِزَار"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is bound;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K, * TA;) i. e. (Msb) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flank;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaASirapN","text_ar":"خَاصِرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A 'Obeyd, Msb, TA,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ka$oHN","text_ar":"كَشْحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) there are two [parts], called together"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaqowaAni","text_ar":"حَقْوَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (A 'Obeyd, TA:) and the ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"waist-wrapper itself that is called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_izaAr","text_ar":"اـِزَار"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, M, Msb, K;) because it is bound upon the [part of the body called]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haqow","text_ar":"حَقْو"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb, * TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiqowN","text_ar":"حِقْوٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M, K;) which MF asserts to be also a var. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaqowN","text_ar":"حَقْوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ka$oHN","text_ar":"كَشْحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; of the dial. of Hudheyl: and in the K is here added, or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place of the tying thereof;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaqowapN","text_ar":"حَقْوَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiqaA='N","text_ar":"حِقَا=ءٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; [the latter written in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaqA'","text_ar":"حَقاء"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but said in the TA to be like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kitaAbN","text_ar":"كِتَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":";] whereas this is the primary signification: (TA:) pl. (of pauc., S, TA)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHoqK","text_ar":"اَحْقٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHoquwN","text_ar":"اَحْقُوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHoqaA='N","text_ar":"اَحْقَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and (of mult., S, TA)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuqiY~N","text_ar":"حُقِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) [originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Huquw~N","text_ar":"حُقُوٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuEuwlN","text_ar":"فُعُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuluwsN","text_ar":"فُلُوسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiqaA='N","text_ar":"حِقَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,) which is pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaqowN","text_ar":"حَقْوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaqowapN","text_ar":"حَقْوَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as well as syn. with the latter in a sense pointed out above. (TA.) Hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaA*a biHaqowihi","text_ar":"عَاذَ بِحَقْوِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He had recourse to him for refuge, protection,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"preservation."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [See an ex. in a verse cited voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"samoEN","text_ar":"سَمْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-  (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part"},{"kind":"text","text":"of an arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which is the place of the feathers:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"slender part of the hinder portion, next the feathers;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA;) or, as in the A,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"below the feathers."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A rugged place elevated above a torrent;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K, TA;) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiqaA='N","text_ar":"حِقَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any place which a water-course reaches:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As, TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaqowapN","text_ar":"حَقْوَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies (assumed tropical:)  the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elevated piece of ground termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"najowap","text_ar":"نَجْوَة"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"but higher, upon which the animals of prey preserve themselves from the torrent;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and its pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiqaA='N","text_ar":"حِقَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) Accord. to En-Nadr, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An elevated piece"},{"kind":"text","text":"of ground;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an acclivity;"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHoqK","text_ar":"اَحْقٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuqiY~N","text_ar":"حُقِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": accord. to Z, (assumed tropical:)  the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"safoH","text_ar":"سَفْح"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lowest part,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"face,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,] of a mountain: (TA:) also (tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"each of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the two sides"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vaniy~apN","text_ar":"ثَنِيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or long mountain traversed by a road; or a part of a mountain that requires one, in traversing it, to ascend and descend; &c.]: (K, TA:) Lth says that when you look at the head of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vaniy~apN","text_ar":"ثَنِيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a"},{"kind":"page_break","n":614},{"kind":"text","text":"mountain, you see its prominence to have what are termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaqowaAni","text_ar":"حَقْوَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","TA","As"]},{"entry_id":"n8660","headword_ar":"حِقْوٌ","root":"Hqw","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaqowN","text_ar":"حَقْوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}